hain.  These flagship programs include: organization", "bbox": [103.1, 1361.8, 1111.9, 1389.2]}, {"text": "excellence; information technology excellence; procurement excellence; service excellence; lab excellence; and billing", "bbox": [103.1, 1386.8, 1099.4, 1414.2]}, {"text": "excellence.  From 2012 through 2014, the Invigorate program was intended to partially offset reimbursement pressures and", "bbox": [103.1, 1411.8, 1134.3, 1439.2]}, {"text": "labor and benefit cost increases; free up additional resources to invest in science, innovation and other growth initiatives; and", "bbox": [103.1, 1436.8, 1151.6, 1464.2]}, {"text": "enable us to improve service quality and operating profitability.", "bbox": [103.1, 1461.8, 642.7, 1489.2]}, {"text": "QUEST DIAGNOSTICS 2016 ANNUAL REPORT ON FORM 10-K", "bbox": [150.0, 1595.0, 617.1, 1616.9]}]}